        Runtime Filter Build: #[-1,0]  𝄀
        ->  Table Scan on func_geometry.spatial_idx_path [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: st_intersects(spatial_idx_path.g, 'POINT(1 1)')  𝄀
              Runtime Filter Probe: spatial_idx_path.id  𝄀
        ->  Index Table Scan on spatial_idx_path.idx_g [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
              Filter Cond: st_intersects(__mo_index_idx_col, 'POINT(1 1)')
